title: Stormy winds whip up 8-10 ft waves on Lake Ontario (video)
text: Oswego, N.Y.-- A storm system the delivered gale force winds, ice and snow throughout Central New York and downed trees and spurred numerous car accidents also produced breath-taking views on Lake Ontario Thursday. Marine advisories for small watercraft were issued as waves ranged...
